{"tid":495063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"3學生扶起跌倒長者　反遭索價10萬元住院費","createTime":"2017-12-10T10:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T09:20:40.000Z","uid":39464,"like":107,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"f715151c0f6e64e388333ac9b0f0161ed38a95d4","tid":495063,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T10:45:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171209/s00004/57bc65aeb0d58c6cd77422c40c89b3ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171209%2Fs00004%2F57bc65aeb0d58c6cd77422c40c89b3ea.jpg&h=d14603e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒報道，上周日（3日），江西上饒一間中學3名學生，在路上見到一名手持拐杖的長者摔倒，趕上前扶起後，對方說是這3名學生踢到她的拐杖令她跌倒，隨即要求付錢買藥，更是由50元、100元、2000元、5000元一路叫上去，最後開價10萬元住院費。3名學生報警。<br />\n<br />\n事件過程被附近街坊拍下，相關片段其後亦在網上廣傳。到周六（9日）下午，當地教育局稱，片段可見3名學生純粹助人，會通報表揚，並由民警上門向學生家長澄清。至於事件中的長者，則是有精神問題。<br />\n<br />\n（江南都市報/澎湃新聞）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171209/s00004/1512834728196\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171209%2Fs00004%2F1512834728196&d=0SiDj62cuN3EJFKh3J%2F8KhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=3839f48f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171209%2Fs00004%2F1512834728196&h=9d6c9a64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171209/s00004/1512834728196</a>"},{"pid":"f9628d7021dad5e92d5824b193151ce373731c6d","tid":495063,"uid":11920,"like":161,"dislike":0,"score":161,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T10:46:48.000Z","msg":"符合蟈蜻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"135cd492c4fcac007a2e4e48a4530b2e059b7338","tid":495063,"uid":116530,"like":86,"dislike":2,"score":84,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T10:48:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>符合蟈蜻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"h